title: 820-3115 green light, then replaced ISL 625 and now fan spins for 2 seconds
message:
Hi there!

have 820-3115 that had corrosion around SIL 625 and only showed green light. . now have replaced that and the fan spins tempoarily and DC power supply indicates that it's going to boots but then goes back to dead

help appriciated

title: 820-3115 green light, then replaced ISL 625 and now fan spins for 2 seconds
message: maybe i should try another ISL?

title: 820-3115 green light, then replaced ISL 625 and now fan spins for 2 seconds
message: Resistance between pins 17/18 and 27/28 of the ISL6259? My bet is liquid messed up your current sensing circuit causing quarter fan spin.

title: 820-3115 green light, then replaced ISL 625 and now fan spins for 2 seconds
message:
AMAZING!!!! I checked resistance between 17/18 and resistance was crazy high. then i checked continuity between pin 18 and c7050 and it had no connection. ran a jumper and BAM it's back. you helped us pay our rent this month.

THANK YOU
